{"tid":1468510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚啲分化割𥱊Post多到痴線 重申一次絕對不割𥱊","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:56:21.000Z","uid":174447,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0a837f243ea160ba5cbed1911421a66e3f4a3f","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:02.000Z","msg":"絕對不割𥱊 只係覺得有野要改善<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好傷害記者同救護員 <br />\n呢個行為錯得理譜 錯到同popo無分別</span><br />\n我明 可能現場環境氣氛導致 或者有<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span><br />\n但真係要Set條底線比自己 <br />\n捉完鬼要挷要私刑 要乜都好 唔好係有記者既環境下做 <br />\n咁呢句係廢話我知 因為實會有記者<br />\n所以好遺憾地 絕大多數情況下係無乜野可以做   <br />\n點解 <span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地打緊正義牌 文宣組一定要打正義牌</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好自己提供黑材料比對家</span></span><br />\n當然私底下尋人 麻包袋 抹黑起底參軍器官捐贈 呢啲就喜聞樂見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實民意我地已經有 過左811已經唔係黃藍而係黑白之分<br />\n但今晚之後文宣組要做返好多PR去解決公關災難<br />\n總之記住我地<span style=\"color: red;\">角色</span>點都要係被壓迫既一方 <br />\nbe humble係好緊要 \b我地共勉之<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師/和理非們 <br />\n唔好下下話輸哂 <br />\n前線popo做幾多柒事 每日出幾多PR災難 <br />\n4點鐘大Sir有無同佢割？無  因為<span style=\"color: red;\">一割就失軍心所以老閪都唔會割</span> <br />\n日日開記者會洗白 幾柒都好至少穩定軍心<br />\n而我地比popo更加進步既點係 <br />\n我地會反省 會認錯 而且我地絕不割𥱊！<br />\n今日既事無大家想像中咁大鑊 失左部分人既民意唔會輸 <br />\n比外國人屌破壞國際形象 唔會輸<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分化 割𥱊 自己搞到自己心灰意冷 呢個先至真正輸 唔好再分化</span><br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師 或者好似我咁事後車大炮既人 <br />\n<strong>be humble <br />\nbe humble<br />\nbe humble</strong><br />\n每一句彈劾都打擊緊前線手足士氣 <br />\n始終佢地先係現場啊<br />\n唔好下下屌同埋屌細力啲啦  <br />\n心急就個個都心急 姐姐我都好撚心急<br />\n但同得中共鬥就預撚左要行好漫長既路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總之 我愛大家 我愛你地機場既每一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"790d15c51d193b405286a195b52b5d9f242514c1","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"05b77e29cb770dd8744bf92d96c531a5504bc80f","tid":1468510,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"3毛比狗屌<br />\n<br />\n【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">試下用 我不會放棄機場 回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/024448_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F024448_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=e8db9d71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/024449_d328056414c9204c8e86b080c75810da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F024449_d328056414c9204c8e86b080c75810da.png&h=7aab3efd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/024450_5f8f6ff36bc67709b006fb3036068dcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F024450_5f8f6ff36bc67709b006fb3036068dcd.png&h=2d2eb638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4265d2ffbcc74f1a28032a769466f4bf8c0c11d3","tid":1468510,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"797adab600ddb8e853fd1decb41096d47a39c220","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bc0aa3f663f3f7b038034bb4982301426badcbfb","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5b54ca6ba321446420e0c813e76e7ee04f63926e","tid":1468510,"uid":99442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:36.000Z","msg":"同意！我愛你地！"},{"pid":"38eecd1e429d4aff755dad206c2e32a86d5d19d9","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"53502ecf56285585e6152061c584d6408848cdb1","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5ffb71b6006324a55f327cceb82479a02afdaf0d","tid":1468510,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jUudSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jUudSB.jpg&h=7ccf2950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7782e1b2552c38e729d2e452632d39be77573a3f","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:49.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7f4fb0e941d5979e28043ff6395f3a1aa6795837","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:42.000Z","msg":"6 瀨屎都唔割！！！"},{"pid":"0fac6fffbe9c7639993f21d41a583b6c1c5660bd","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"1ef4fd6e0b5500249771e43c1169ac7dc6cd10de","tid":1468510,"uid":206546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住所有手足共識：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼正確方法 (PR最好睇)<br />\n1. 詢問<br />\n2. 控制，防止逃跑<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">搵記者，由記者盤問（811記者問黑警扮示威者咁樣）</span></strong><br />\n5. 睇證件、影相<br />\n6. <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">散開，不包圍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n721 805 811</span>"},{"pid":"17e503f6c936b85870b25c9f47c6aaaf74c64699","tid":1468510,"uid":47898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:15.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"41c3ebfb9f8cdc1c606e4ba20344773d98a4f072","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9a0da1c0e3a6ef4dbb5e33801e6412c944fd6d9d","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d080ff9a2f42495648e1414f00ead391934f44a4","tid":1468510,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeedd37d4169c167e4d7168b03e110a7207299c","tid":1468510,"uid":174447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"10 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">I love you all </span>"},{"pid":"2f55efa09759483c2b4d3dc4a4733ed853b80267","tid":1468510,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:27.000Z","msg":"right"},{"pid":"1ef3a0656e556fc3248c20a7b0ddc7710cdd9ccc","tid":1468510,"uid":28892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:02.000Z","msg":"我希望大家可以保持我地係「受害者」喱個身份。<br />\n<br />\n有喱個身份保護我地做咩都有人同情，就算俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n都會屌得細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n一旦我地變成「加害者」，我地做錯少少都會無限<br />\n<br />\n放大。<br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟，我地登報做文宣都係想塑造形象俾人<br />\n<br />\n睇，我地需要有大義喺手。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭要打壓我地都要屈我地係港獨先啦。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨玩權鬥都要話自己係打貪。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以冷靜思考下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4143132939c4f1eef5f1a1070f2612cc25a78fe","tid":1468510,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6652331b37939893ef9702ab5914ad757f25f1","tid":1468510,"uid":120729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"大家停止互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗補救措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再沉迷捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eee12bad1f80a7cf4a1e42169a63696dc40260f","tid":1468510,"uid":292429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:33.000Z","msg":"係要出返呢啲正能量post先得<br />\n其實今晚件事係畫面唔係幾好睇之外<br />\n又有咩咁大不了呢<br />\n值得嘈黎嘈去咩？<br />\n認真 學下何妖死都唔割牛屎佬既堅持<br />\n就算係痴線佬都真係有值得學習既地方"},{"pid":"035fd58fd14742f9e59d0b6cca39370bf9eca8c2","tid":1468510,"uid":143708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:12:31.000Z","msg":"太多五毛做嘢<br />\n每次有呢啲post就無視/<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用不推文功能</span><br />\n可以用返不割席 不分化 或者討論嘅post洗走啲五毛post<br />\n唔好比人帶到風向"}]}